reviewText: Does Randy wrestle Radimus on this DVD?

the dvd is something special....macho man randy savage  was an incredible performer, he made u' hate him or love him!!!! his days in the outlaw promotion known as international championship wrestling aka icw, just before jerry jarrett called him to wrestle in memphis!!! my most favorite match on the dvd is ron garvin vs. randy savage..steel cage match...it's off the meat rack!!!!
